            <div CLASS="church"><span CLASS="side-head">Our Church</span></div>
            <div CLASS="about-description">
                VC3 is a Church that loves Jesus Christ and is passionate about loving people. We believe that the world needs Church now more than any time before, and it is time for the Church to go beyond its walls reaching to every man outside. We believe that the message of God’s saving grace to man remains eternal but the Church is called to make this Gospel relevant to this generation. We are a Church filled with faith, love to worship God and love his Word. VC3 now is a vibrant Church filled with people passionate for God and serving God wherever they are placed.
            </div>
            <div CLASS="vision"><span CLASS="side-head">Our Vision</span></div>
            <div CLASS="about-description">
                "To build a church that is relevant to this generation and to be a positive influence on the society."
            
            </div>
            <div CLASS="leaders">
                <span CLASS="side-head">Our Leaders</span>
                <div CLASS="back-top mobile-image" STYLE="background-image: url(../../Images/about-pagebanner-leaders.jpg)"></div>
                <%--<div class="mobile-image" style="background-image: url()"></div>--%>
                <%--<img src="../../Images/about-pagebanner-leaders.jpg" style="display: block; width: 100%; margin-top: 30px; max-width: 1200px; margin: 30px auto;" />--%>
                <div CLASS="about-description">
                    Pastor Sumanth Perumalla has been passionately serving God past few decades in numerous capacities and through various ministries. Prior to planting VC3, Pastor Sumanth has served as an Executive Pastor of a Church responsible for pastoral care, cell groups, a Bible college and numerous satellite churches. Pastor Sumanth heard the voice of God while working in IBM after his MBA, and responded by coming into full time Ministry. Pastor Sumanth is highly regarded as a speaker and leader who can connect to this generation and speak hope.
                <br />
                    Pastor Rani Perumalla grew up as a Roman Catholic and was born again during her schooling. Leading a passionate life in God she was part of the worship team and was actively involved in cell groups, and youth ministry. Pastor Rani completed her B.Ed and worked as a headmistress before her marriage with Pastor Sumanth Perumalla and joined active ministry. Pastor Rani has a passionate heart towards building the church and initiates Women’s ministry in VC3.Pastors Sumanth and Rani Perumalla, apart from serving as Senior Ministers of VC3, regularly travel to numerous countries each year on ministerial visits and to train leaders. Further encompassing their ministerial commitments Ps. Sumanth and Rani Perumalla also have ventures in Publishing and Business Solutions, providing process solutions to International companies. Pastors Sumanth and Rani Perumalla are blessed with two daughters, Elisa Christine and Cheryl Judith.
                </div>
            </div>
