            <div CLASS="about-description">
                <div CLASS="scripture">There is one God: God The Father, God The Son, God The Holy Spirit.</div>
                <div CLASS="reference"><a HREF="#" TARGET="_blank">Deuteronomy 6:4</a><a HREF="#" TARGET="_blank">Mathew 28:19</a></div>
                <div CLASS="scripture">In the deity of our Lord Jesus Christ the Son of God; we believe in His virgin birth, in His sinless life, in His miracles, in His vicarious and atoning death, in His bodily resurrection, in His ascension to the right hand of the Father, His constant intercession and in His imminent return.</div>
                <div CLASS="reference"><a HREF="#" TARGET="_blank">Isaiah 7:14</a><a HREF="#" TARGET="_blank">Ephesians 1:20-22</a>; <a HREF="#" TARGET="_blank">Hebrews 7:25</a></div>
                <div CLASS="scripture">The Bible is the Living Word of God - infaliable, authoritative and everlasting, and the foundation of all Christian doctrine.</div>
                <div CLASS="reference"><a HREF="#" TARGET="_blank">2 Timothy 3:16</a></div>
